syntax on "Turn on syntax highlighting

set cursorline      "Outline the line the current cursor position is on.
set expandtab       "Tabs expand to spaces.
set ignorecase      "Ignore case when searching, but use with smart case so searches including capitals do search by case.`
set history=1000    "Store 1000 entires in history, the default is 20.
set hlsearch        "Highlight matches during a search.
set relativenumber  "Display line numbers relative to the current cursor position.
set smartcase       "Override ignorecase when searches contain capitals.
set tabstop=4       "Tabs are 4 spaces wide".